HEADWORD: Monstrosity
<hw>Mon*stros"i*ty</hw> <pr>(m⟦ocr⟧n*str⟦ocr⟧s"⟦icr⟧*t⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Monstrosities</plw>
